Today, we are surrounded by an excess of electromagnetic fields, with cell phones, iPads, and computers interfering with our natural electric currents. Electromagnetic fields (EMFs) are all around us, and research indicates a rise in cancer rates due to radiation exposure. This silent killer's frequencies are invisible to the naked eye. Discover Russia's simple guidelines on EMFs. Join us in this short video and discover what we can do to protect our health and prevent diseases caused by these devices!
